{"tid":247851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"13人涉管有兒童色情物品 警撿2萬張相片+7千套影片","createTime":"2017-05-18T06:31:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T10:27:42.000Z","uid":38886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eadd9dbfa2691d2a8ee02680a4b164486b254ade","tid":247851,"uid":38886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T06:31:42.000Z","msg":"警方網絡安全及科技罪案調查科，<br />\n拘捕13名男子涉嫌管有兒童色情物品。<br />\n<br />\n警方網絡安全及科技罪案調查科(行動組)高級督察范俊業稱，警方採取代號「跨欄」行動，突擊搜查全港多個地點，拘捕共13名男子，他們年齡由20至46歲，撿獲2萬張涉及兒童色情的照片及7千多套影片，行動仍然繼續。不排除再有人被捕。不過相信他們為獨立人士，並沒有集團的操控。<br />\n<br />\n范俊業續稱，疑犯從不同渠道取得該些照片和影片，包括上網購買、下載及透過分享軟件，然後存儲在電腦內。他提醒稱，管有兒童色情物品，最高可判入獄5年及罰款100萬元。警方會繼續與海外執法機構合作，打擊相關罪行。而2016年同類的案件有43宗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81dc1d3ebc649cc901cec5ce2f3fbb913f8ab5ba","tid":247851,"uid":2445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T06:33:55.000Z","msg":"范俊業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad5c6b20f2e0679d46cc4205ff7f72c1e164201","tid":247851,"uid":38886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T06:34:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>范俊業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好型仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ec7d7a0ed4c4846552d1fda5db296681e9a4fe","tid":247851,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T06:41:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc5861b4433142444f1cc7c5b1590befe5187ae9","tid":247851,"uid":38886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T06:56:58.000Z","msg":"其實警察係點樣查到自己電腦有禁相架呢？"},{"pid":"3c5727f9803e92f25a4e6d8fa0066ef1269e0ce6","tid":247851,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:07:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實警察係點樣查到自己電腦有禁相架呢？</blockquote><br />\n會唔會咸網提供ip address"},{"pid":"eb9c74336af866c09f7a3f95097a7ed50a0dc0f7","tid":247851,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:16:09.000Z","msg":"喂上面，兒童色情定義好似係不足16歲，<br />\n唔係18歲喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fddc0f3b413bdfdffe28b7dadb235f21b1ad33b","tid":247851,"uid":38886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:25:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實警察係點樣查到自己電腦有禁相架呢？</blockquote><br />\n會唔會咸網提供ip address</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nWhere is the site?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e9f0284d3e4e78cf8ca66f2da6f011b897d028","tid":247851,"uid":16453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:55:57.000Z","msg":"P2P 係咪check到？"},{"pid":"d85979bb86a830d85ba292f6ff1060d630b74a91","tid":247851,"uid":64504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T09:58:15.000Z","msg":"專登放蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df95f9871da649b0e2069bad2efe04aabdd7b610","tid":247851,"uid":2590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:27:42.000Z","msg":"好慘，俾人砌生豬肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小市民down av唔小心down錯都可能俾人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}